## About glow

[glow](https://github.com/charmbracelet/glow) is a charmbracelet CLI
that renders Markdown files in the terminal. It's a *binary* — there
is no Go import; you install it once with `go install
github.com/charmbracelet/glow/v2@latest` and shell out to it.

## Usage

```sh
glow README.md            # render the README in the terminal
glow --pager README.md    # paginate long docs
glow --style dark README.md
```

